817
00:46:30,078 --> 00:46:31,205
I guess so.

818
00:46:33,790 --> 00:46:34,875
I guess so.

819
00:46:39,713 --> 00:46:40,631
Good night.

820
00:46:41,882 --> 00:46:42,758
Bye.

821
00:46:43,842 --> 00:46:45,427
-Good night.
-Good night.

