988
00:57:23,064 --> 00:57:24,274
Tofu-of-edge face?

989
00:57:25,066 --> 00:57:29,195
Even though he's the opposite
of my ideal type,

990
00:57:29,821 --> 00:57:33,575
he was such a good person

991
00:57:33,658 --> 00:57:35,910
that I became attracted to him.

992
00:57:38,163 --> 00:57:41,332
I'm going to ask
where Jun-seung got his ring.

993
00:57:41,916 --> 00:57:43,835
<i>Even though someone is your ideal type,</i>

994
00:57:43,918 --> 00:57:46,629
<i>you can become friends with them.</i>

995
00:57:48,131 --> 00:57:50,175
<i>Or maybe not.</i>

996
00:57:57,390 --> 00:57:58,683
I really didn't see this coming.

997
00:57:58,766 --> 00:57:59,601
You didn't?

998
00:58:01,227 --> 00:58:02,061
I had no clue.

999
00:58:02,770 --> 00:58:03,897
How could I know?

1000
00:58:07,358 --> 00:58:09,152
You didn't tell me, so how would I know?

1001
00:58:10,570 --> 00:58:13,531
SI-HYUN, READ YOUR LETTER
AND CONFESS YOUR FEELINGS

1002
00:58:13,615 --> 00:58:17,452
"From the moment I went down
to pick you up from the Isolated House

1003
00:58:17,535 --> 00:58:19,537
to before our date yesterday,

1004
00:58:19,621 --> 00:58:23,541
you were someone who I was curious about
and made my heart flutter."

1005
00:58:23,625 --> 00:58:24,667
"After our date yesterday,

1006
00:58:24,751 --> 00:58:26,794
my feelings for you grew."

1007
00:58:26,878 --> 00:58:28,546
Out there, it had to be

1008
00:58:28,630 --> 00:58:31,549
"love at first sight" for me
to get into a relationship with someone.

1009
00:58:31,633 --> 00:58:34,385
But because she showed
how much she likes me,

1010
00:58:34,469 --> 00:58:35,720
my feelings for her grew as well.

1011
00:58:36,930 --> 00:58:39,182
<i>When I was taking pictures of her,</i>

1012
00:58:39,265 --> 00:58:41,601
<i>she looked pretty through the viewfinder.</i>

1013
00:58:43,353 --> 00:58:45,647
<i>Because we got along so well,</i>

1014
00:58:46,147 --> 00:58:49,192
even though she wasn't
completely my type looks-wise,

1015
00:58:49,275 --> 00:58:52,612
I was able to develop feelings for her.

1016
00:58:52,695 --> 00:58:54,614
"Thank you for showing
how much you like me,

1017
00:58:54,697 --> 00:58:56,282
and I was thrilled and happy too."

1018
00:58:56,366 --> 00:58:58,660
"I couldn't show you
how much I liked you here,

1019
00:58:58,743 --> 00:59:00,537
and I made you worry a lot,

1020
00:59:00,620 --> 00:59:02,914
but let's get out of here
and be happy together."

1021
00:59:12,549 --> 00:59:15,760
CONGRATULATIONS ON BEING THE FINAL MATCH
HOLD HANDS AND DESCEND THE MOUNTAIN

1022
00:59:27,939 --> 00:59:29,190
What was that?

1023
00:59:29,274 --> 00:59:30,149
What?

1024
00:59:42,287 --> 00:59:44,080
SI-HYUN WAS HESITANT
WITH ONE HEART CHIP IN HAND LAST NIGHT

1025
00:59:45,039 --> 00:59:47,959
BUT HE USED UP HIS HEART CHIPS IN THE END

1026
00:59:49,002 --> 00:59:52,130
AND GAVE A TOTAL OF 180 HEART CHIPS
TO JI-YOUNG OVER 3 DAYS

1027
00:59:52,213 --> 00:59:54,966
FOR 3 NIGHTS AND 4 DAYS, 4 SUBJECTS WERE
ISOLATED WITH THEIR IDEAL TYPES

1028
00:59:55,049 --> 00:59:57,093
I'm more drawn to cat-like features.

1029
00:59:58,511 --> 01:00:00,930
<i>My ideal type was walking toward me.</i>

1030
01:00:01,431 --> 01:00:03,182
"Don't feel too pressured."

1031
01:00:03,266 --> 01:00:04,934
"Come eat <i>hoe </i>with me too."

1032
01:00:06,144 --> 01:00:07,979
I also like the edge-of-tofu face.

1033
01:00:08,062 --> 01:00:09,314
Me? I'm the edge-of-tofu.

1034
01:00:09,397 --> 01:00:11,649
JI-YOUNG, WHO WANTED TO MEET
AN EDGE-OF-TOFU FACE, CHOSE SI-HYUN

1035
01:00:11,733 --> 01:00:13,026
<i>Once-in-a-millennium ideal type.</i>

1036
01:00:13,109 --> 01:00:15,194
"Let's leave together. You have to enjoy
the 'Ji-young view' again."

1037
01:00:17,405 --> 01:00:20,992
Hyun-jin was closer
to my ideal type in terms of looks.

1038
01:00:21,075 --> 01:00:22,493
You'll find out when you get there.

1039
01:00:22,577 --> 01:00:24,162
SI-HYUN, WHOSE IDEAL TYPE IS HYUN-JIN,
CHOSE JI-YOUNG

1040
01:00:24,245 --> 01:00:26,372
Because we got along so well,

1041
01:00:26,456 --> 01:00:29,417
even though she wasn't
completely my type looks-wise,

1042
01:00:29,500 --> 01:00:32,920
I was able to develop feelings for her.

1043
01:00:33,004 --> 01:00:36,382
What I'm sure about is
that an edge-of-tofu face is not my type.

1044
01:00:37,675 --> 01:00:39,093
I like you.

1045
01:00:39,177 --> 01:00:41,429
HYUN-JIN CHOSE SI-HYUN,
WHO WAS IN LAST PLACE OF HER IDEAL TYPES

1046
01:00:42,096 --> 01:00:45,141
I realized the looks I thought I wanted

1047
01:00:46,059 --> 01:00:47,185
didn't really matter.

1048
01:00:47,268 --> 01:00:50,563
I think it'd be okay <i>because</i> it's him.

1049
01:00:50,647 --> 01:00:53,566
JUN-SEUNG AND JI-YOUNG CHOSE
THEIR IDEAL TYPE

1050
01:00:53,650 --> 01:00:56,611
SI-HYUN AND HYUN-JIN CHOSE
SOMEONE WHO ISN'T THEIR IDEAL TYPE

1051
01:00:57,862 --> 01:01:01,491
IF YOU'RE ISOLATED WITH YOUR IDEAL TYPE,
WOULD YOU FALL FOR THEM?

1052
01:01:01,574 --> 01:01:05,536
EXPERIMENT RESULT
THERE'S A 50% CHANCE YOU'LL FALL IN LOVE

1053
01:01:05,620 --> 01:01:06,954
What do you want to eat the most?

1054
01:01:07,038 --> 01:01:08,539
I want to eat some meat.

1055
01:01:08,623 --> 01:01:10,166
I want pork cutlet too.

1056
01:01:12,126 --> 01:01:15,421
This feels so unreal.
We went up together on the first day.

1057
01:01:15,505 --> 01:01:16,547
I know.

1058
01:01:16,631 --> 01:01:18,091
Now we're going down together.

1059
01:01:19,592 --> 01:01:20,468
We're escaping.

1060
01:01:20,551 --> 01:01:22,136
-Yeah, we're really escaping.
-Yeah.

1061
01:01:22,845 --> 01:01:24,097
The mailbox.

1062
01:01:24,180 --> 01:01:25,932
I haven't seen it in four days.

1063
01:01:26,432 --> 01:01:28,726
-My number is…
-Okay.

1064
01:01:28,810 --> 01:01:30,520
-What did you save me as?
-Ji-young View.

1065
01:01:32,271 --> 01:01:35,108
So are you the icon
of edge-of-tofu face now?

1066
01:01:35,733 --> 01:01:36,859
I suppose so.

1067
01:01:37,485 --> 01:01:39,946
AFTER THE SHOOT

1068
01:01:40,029 --> 01:01:41,989
JI-YOUNG AND SI-HYUN'S DATE

1069
01:01:42,073 --> 01:01:44,075
THEY WENT TO SEE
THE CHERRY BLOSSOMS TOGETHER

1070
01:01:44,158 --> 01:01:45,159
It's Si-hyun.

1071
01:01:45,243 --> 01:01:46,327
JI-YOUNG FOUND HER IDEAL TYPE

1072
01:01:46,411 --> 01:01:47,995
The edge of tofu.

1073
01:01:49,997 --> 01:01:53,710
JUN-SEUNG WENT ON A LONG-AWAITED DATE
WITH JI-YOUNG IN SEOUL TOO

1074
01:01:53,793 --> 01:01:55,837
-No way.
-What?

1075
01:01:58,798 --> 01:02:00,049
-What?
-What's happening?

1076
01:02:02,343 --> 01:02:03,594
They didn't end up dating.

1077
01:02:03,678 --> 01:02:05,638
I told you it isn't over until it's over.

1078
01:02:05,722 --> 01:02:07,807
She wouldn't go on a date with him
if she's official with Si-hyun.

1079
01:02:07,890 --> 01:02:09,684
-Wait.
-They're not together.

1080
01:02:09,767 --> 01:02:12,145
-What's going on?
-She said, "Edge of tofu."

1081
01:02:13,730 --> 01:02:15,356
She said, "Edge of tofu."

1082
01:02:15,440 --> 01:02:16,649
Look.

1083
01:02:16,733 --> 01:02:18,526
That was all in one day.

1084
01:02:18,609 --> 01:02:20,194
Things almost worked out between them,

1085
01:02:20,278 --> 01:02:22,321
but something went wrong,
and it didn't work out.

1086
01:02:22,405 --> 01:02:24,949
Then, Jun-seung found an in
and asked to meet up with her.

1087
01:02:25,825 --> 01:02:28,161
So they met up. This is insane.

1088
01:02:28,244 --> 01:02:29,537
Let's watch a bit more.

1089
01:02:29,620 --> 01:02:30,455
Wait.

1090
01:02:31,080 --> 01:02:32,623
Are they in Seongsu?

1091
01:02:32,707 --> 01:02:34,500
-Isn't it Anguk?
-Is it Anguk?

1092
01:02:35,918 --> 01:02:37,587
Didn't you wear something like this?

1093
01:02:38,379 --> 01:02:39,213
This color?

1094
01:02:39,297 --> 01:02:40,965
It'd look nice
if you wore something underneath.

1095
01:02:41,048 --> 01:02:43,301
PICKING OUT CLOTHES FOR EACH OTHER

1096
01:02:43,885 --> 01:02:45,052
This is on a different day!

1097
01:02:45,678 --> 01:02:48,264
He's picking out clothes for her,
so maybe she changed shirts.

1098
01:02:48,347 --> 01:02:49,640
Look at their jewelry.

1099
01:02:49,724 --> 01:02:50,725
Wait.

1100
01:02:51,809 --> 01:02:53,478
He wasn't wearing a bracelet!

1101
01:02:53,561 --> 01:02:55,062
But he's wearing a bracelet here.

1102
01:02:55,146 --> 01:02:56,397
Those are two different days.

1103
01:02:58,816 --> 01:03:00,401
EATING A SWEET DESSERT AT A CAFE

1104
01:03:00,485 --> 01:03:01,944
It looks so sweet.

1105
01:03:02,028 --> 01:03:03,905
This one is awesome. Try it.

1106
01:03:03,988 --> 01:03:05,156
I'll try this one first.

1107
01:03:09,285 --> 01:03:15,374
GOING ON A DATE BY HANGANG RIVER
INSTEAD OF THE BEACH IN GANGNEUNG

1108
01:03:16,793 --> 01:03:21,964
HYUN-JIN AND SI-HYUN'S HIKE

1109
01:03:22,048 --> 01:03:25,134
Of the four of us,
who will start dating first?

1110
01:03:25,218 --> 01:03:26,636
Honestly, I think it's Hyun-jin.

1111
01:03:26,719 --> 01:03:28,221
-Me.
-Me too.

1112
01:03:28,846 --> 01:03:30,431
I think it's me too.

1113
01:03:30,515 --> 01:03:32,558
I think Hyun-jin will start dating first.

1114
01:03:32,642 --> 01:03:33,601
I think it'll be me.

1115
01:03:33,684 --> 01:03:35,019
That's going to make me sad.

1116
01:03:36,395 --> 01:03:38,272
Come on. Stop messing around.

1117
01:03:38,356 --> 01:03:39,315
Who is it?

1118
01:03:40,024 --> 01:03:41,150
Unbelievable.

1119
01:03:41,734 --> 01:03:43,236
Hey, turn off the camera.

1120
01:03:43,319 --> 01:03:45,863
-Why?
-Let's not date since we're all busy.

1121
01:03:46,823 --> 01:03:48,783
I’m not going to date anyone
before Si-hyun does.

1122
01:03:48,866 --> 01:03:51,118
Si-hyun? I think Si-hyun will…

1123
01:03:51,202 --> 01:03:53,496
<i>If Si-hyun starts dating someone…</i>

1124
01:03:53,579 --> 01:03:54,705
THEIR OWN LOVE LAB EXPERIMENT CONTINUES

1125
01:03:55,289 --> 01:03:58,209
What the heck? Why would they
ask a question like that?

1126
01:03:58,793 --> 01:04:01,003
People these days are amazing.

1127
01:04:01,087 --> 01:04:03,089
They're shooting a dating show
even without a camera rolling.

1128
01:04:03,673 --> 01:04:05,049
How is that possible?

1129
01:04:05,132 --> 01:04:06,843
I'm being serious.

1130
01:04:06,926 --> 01:04:08,845
This was the most
entertaining thing I saw today.

1131
01:04:08,928 --> 01:04:09,929
Their self-cam.

1132
01:04:10,012 --> 01:04:11,639
Man, that was awesome.

1133
01:04:11,722 --> 01:04:14,267
Look, it isn't over until it's over!

1134
01:04:14,350 --> 01:04:17,144
This should be implemented
on other dating shows too.

1135
01:04:17,228 --> 01:04:18,855
Participants filming themselves
even after the shoot.

1136
01:04:18,938 --> 01:04:21,482
This was so fun. This is insane!

1137
01:04:21,566 --> 01:04:22,650
This is what I like.

1138
01:04:22,733 --> 01:04:24,902
Everyone’s interested,
but they’re all acting indifferent.

1139
01:04:24,986 --> 01:04:26,696
-They're acting like friends.
-This is so fun.

1140
01:04:29,574 --> 01:04:30,783
They're just like me.

1141
01:04:31,784 --> 01:04:34,912
"Who's going to date first?"
But she's thinking, "I want to date you."

1142
01:04:34,996 --> 01:04:36,664
''I think it's definitely Si-hyun."

1143
01:04:36,747 --> 01:04:39,458
-Nothing that they say is truthful.
-Right?

1144
01:04:39,542 --> 01:04:42,879
If Jun-seung didn't give up
and kept hitting on her,

1145
01:04:42,962 --> 01:04:44,463
she might change her mind.

1146
01:04:45,047 --> 01:04:47,008
What about Jun-seung and Hyun-jin?

1147
01:04:47,091 --> 01:04:48,467
I want them to end up together.

1148
01:04:48,551 --> 01:04:51,053
That would be juicier.
From friends to lovers.

1149
01:04:51,137 --> 01:04:54,098
The real-life Sung Si-won
and Yoon Yoon-je.

1150
01:04:54,181 --> 01:04:57,143
Friend? Whatever.
The title should be "Friend? Whatever."

1151
01:04:59,729 --> 01:05:01,731
I'm so curious about the next experiment.

1152
01:05:02,607 --> 01:05:04,442
<i>The third Love Lab experiment is</i>

1153
01:05:05,651 --> 01:05:07,528
<i>Drunk Blind Date.</i>

1154
01:05:07,612 --> 01:05:08,571
Shall we clink glasses?

1155
01:05:09,572 --> 01:05:13,910
<i>Melting away the looks, backgrounds,</i>
<i>and circumstances in alcohol,</i>

1156
01:05:14,493 --> 01:05:19,498
<i>the man and woman must face each other</i>
<i>only in their drunk state.</i>

1157
01:05:19,582 --> 01:05:21,709
<i>Women who are cold but pretty…</i>

1158
01:05:21,792 --> 01:05:22,627
<i>I'm nervous.</i>

1159
01:05:22,710 --> 01:05:23,920
<i>Am I his ideal type?</i>

1160
01:05:24,003 --> 01:05:26,297
<i>Do you believe in fated love?</i>

1161
01:05:26,380 --> 01:05:29,550
<i>I don't know if I'm drawn to him</i>
<i>because of the alcohol…</i>

1162
01:05:29,634 --> 01:05:33,012
For my next relationship,
I want to meet someone established.

1163
01:05:33,095 --> 01:05:34,013
That's me.

1164
01:05:34,096 --> 01:05:37,099
<i>Does alcohol really help with dating?</i>

1165
01:05:37,183 --> 01:05:38,517
In this place…

1166
01:05:38,601 --> 01:05:41,103
<i>-Or will it be an obstacle instead?</i>
-It was fun.

1167
01:05:41,187 --> 01:05:42,772
<i>I think it's fate</i>

1168
01:05:43,356 --> 01:05:44,190
that I met you.

1169
01:05:50,863 --> 01:05:52,865
Subtitle translation by: Ilyoung Kim

1170
01:05:52,949 --> 01:05:55,451
THE LOVE LAB
